==Geography==
[[File:Zorro-panorama.jpg|thumb|650px|none|Panoramic view from Leirfjord]]
The municipality of Leirfjord is centered around the [[Leirfjorden]], with most of the municipality on the mainland and a small part on the northeastern part of the island of [[Alsta]].  The [[Sund<U+00F8>y Bridge]] connects the mainland to the northeastern part of the island of [[Alsta]] and the [[Helgeland Bridge]] connects it to the rest of Alsta and the town of Sandnessj<U+00F8>en.  The [[Ranfjorden]] runs along the northern part of Leirfjord and the [[Vefsnfjorden]] runs along the southern part of the municipality.

